OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mix of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers, the showers not as heavy as
OL,7,Fprevious days and will become fewer
OL,8,Fand further between through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Still rather cold with an
OL,10,Foccasionally strong northerly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,13,Fclear spells overnight, with showers,
OL,14,Fthese becoming fewer and increasingly
OL,15,Fconfined to northern parts and the
OL,16,FIsles. Touch of frost in sheltered
OL,17,Fparts. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
